description: The style of PIP boxes we offer in our range have a huge variety of uses but have proved the box of choice for eCommerce, mailing and fulfillment companies. They are frequently used for posting and distributing pharmaceutical, clothing, gift, cosmetic, ornamental, and promotional products. They are manufactured primarily from single wall cardboard with a high quality white or brown coating to make packages stand-out and look more presentable. For many businesses it's important that your products and your brand are not just well packaged, but that the packaging itself is representative of the quality of your products. High quality white or brown postal boxes not only offer great protection but also give the perception of quality when your customers receive their delivery improving the overall experience for your customers.
